    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain a second breath weapon. When you take the Attack action on your turn, you can replace one of your attacks with an exhalation in a 15-foot cone. The save DC is equal to your Breath Weapon.</p><p>Each creature in the cone must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or become incapacitated until the start of your next turn.</p><p>You can use this trait a number of times equal to half your proficiency bonus (rounded up), regaining all expended uses when you finish a long rest</p><blockquote><p><strong>When you get this feature, you can choose to update the saving throw DC from Constitution to Charisma if applicable based on your Breath Weapon DC.</strong></p></blockquote>",
